classesOfService.name: FieldView Portland (iOS)
classesOfService.queryForClosed: SELECT [System.Id] FROM WorkItems WHERE [System.AreaPath] = 'FieldView\iOS'  AND  [System.WorkItemType] IN ('User Story', 'Bug')  AND  [System.State] = 'Closed' and [Microsoft.VSTS.Common.ClosedDate] > @today - 183
classesOfService.queryForAll: SELECT [System.Id] FROM WorkItems WHERE [System.AreaPath] = 'FieldView\iOS'  AND  [System.WorkItemType] IN ('User Story', 'Bug')
